dct_description_sm: There is no personal attribution for the map, nor are place, publisher or date indicated. Date is estimated as ca. 1860 as Monrovia is indicated, meaning the date of publication must have been after the town's establishment in 1857, but before 1869, as the Suez Canal had not yet been constructed. The sheet may have been extracted from an atlas.
